Poor Maps 0.9
=============

 [X] Add framework to list nearby services (restaurants, etc.)
 [X] Add Nominatim providers for listing nearby services
 [X] Allow tapping on POI markers to show description
 [X] Add option for the MapQuest Open router to try to avoid tolls
 [ ] Show an error message when connection times out

Poor Maps 1.0
=============

 * Add Foursquare and Yelp providers for listing nearby services
   (assuming their terms of use are reasonable)
 * Add auto-rotate on bearing when the Map component supports it
 * Allow landscape for the map page when gestures work right
 * Add option to prevent sleep while navigating (nemo-keepalive?)
 * Save pagestack to allow returning to geocoding or routing results
 * Allow layered tilesources (traffic, hillshade, etc.)
 * Add user interface translations (strings in QML, Python and JSON
   files as well narrative returned by routing APIs)
 * Add support for non-SI units (miles, etc.)
   - http://stackoverflow.com/a/14044413
